{"title":"旋转数组","slug":"旋转数组","date":"2019-08-07T11:17:23.000Z","updated":"2019-08-07T12:23:10.844Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/旋转数组.json","photos":[],"link":"","excerpt":"#leetcode题目：旋转数组<br>题目描述：<br>给定一个数组，例如[1,2,3,4,5,6,7]，同时给定一个K值，表示数组的向右旋转程度，例如当k等于3时，旋转一次为：[7,1,2,3,4,5,6],旋转第二次为：[6,7,1,2,3,4,5],第三次也就是结果输出为：[5,6,7,1,2,3,4]。<br>","covers":["/2019/08/07/旋转数组/img.png","/2019/08/07/旋转数组/image.png"],"content":"<p>#leetcode题目：旋转数组<br>题目描述：<br>给定一个数组，例如[1,2,3,4,5,6,7]，同时给定一个K值，表示数组的向右旋转程度，例如当k等于3时，旋转一次为：[7,1,2,3,4,5,6],旋转第二次为：[6,7,1,2,3,4,5],第三次也就是结果输出为：[5,6,7,1,2,3,4]。<br><a id=\"more\"></a><br><img src=\"/2019/08/07/旋转数组/img.png\" alt=\"image\"></p>\n<p>##解法一：暴力解法<br>双重循环将数组内的元素进行移位：先将数组最左边的元素取出来，然后其他元素右移，再将取出来的元素放置在数组的第一个位置，循环K次即可。<br><figure class=\"highlight plain\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br><span class=\"line\">11</span><br><span class=\"line\">12</span><br><span class=\"line\">13</span><br><span class=\"line\">14</span><br><span class=\"line\">15</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">class Solution:</span><br><span class=\"line\">    def rotate(self, nums: List[int], k: int) -&gt; None:</span><br><span class=\"line\">        &quot;&quot;&quot;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        Do not return anything, modify nums in-place instead.</span><br><span class=\"line\">        &quot;&quot;&quot;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        i = len(nums);</span><br><span class=\"line\">        t = i-2;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        while(k&gt;0):</span><br><span class=\"line\">            temp = nums[i-1];</span><br><span class=\"line\">            while(t&gt;=0):</span><br><span class=\"line\">                nums[t+1]=nums[t];</span><br><span class=\"line\">                t-=1;</span><br><span class=\"line\">            nums[0]=temp;</span><br><span class=\"line\">            t=i-2;</span><br><span class=\"line\">            k-=1;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>\n<p>时间复杂度：O(NK)<br>空间复杂度：O(1)</p>\n<p>##解法二：利用数组存储<br>将数组中的后K位取出来，存储在另外一个数组中，再将新数组的元素逐个插入原数组的前面位置即可：<br><figure class=\"highlight plain\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br><span class=\"line\">11</span><br><span class=\"line\">12</span><br><span class=\"line\">13</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">class Solution:</span><br><span class=\"line\">    def rotate(self, nums: List[int], k: int) -&gt; None:</span><br><span class=\"line\">        &quot;&quot;&quot;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        Do not return anything, modify nums in-place instead.</span><br><span class=\"line\">        &quot;&quot;&quot;     </span><br><span class=\"line\">        i=0</span><br><span class=\"line\">        tempNums=[];</span><br><span class=\"line\">        for each in nums[len(nums)-k:len(nums)]:</span><br><span class=\"line\">            tempNums.append(each);</span><br><span class=\"line\">            nums.pop();</span><br><span class=\"line\">        for each in tempNums:</span><br><span class=\"line\">            nums.insert(i,each);</span><br><span class=\"line\">            i+=1;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>\n<p>时间复杂度：O(N)<br>空间复杂度：O(N)</p>\n<p>##解法三：将数组逆置<br>例如：1234567-&gt;7654321-&gt;5671234即可<br>时间复杂度：O(N)<br>空间复杂度：O(1)</p>\n<p>##解法四：利用队列的性质<br>将数值的后K个(队尾)依次取出，再依次添加到队头<br><figure class=\"highlight plain\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">class Solution:</span><br><span class=\"line\">    def rotate(self, nums: List[int], k: int) -&gt; None:</span><br><span class=\"line\">        &quot;&quot;&quot;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        Do not return anything, modify nums in-place instead.</span><br><span class=\"line\">        &quot;&quot;&quot;   </span><br><span class=\"line\">        k=k%len(nums);</span><br><span class=\"line\">        i=0;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        while(i&lt;len(nums)-k):</span><br><span class=\"line\">            nums.append(nums.pop(0));</span><br><span class=\"line\">            i+=1;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>\n<p>时间复杂度：O(N)<br>空间复杂度：O(1)</p>\n<p>##解法五：环状替换<br>这是比较难理解的一个方法，首先，如果我们用之前的元素直接去替换它所应该最终在的位置上的元素（原位置+K%N就是它最终应该所在的位置），必然导致元素的丢失，所以，需要用一个变量(temp)先保存起来被替换的元素，继续这个过程N次即可，因为每个元素都要换位置，所以需要这个过程N次。但是有一个问题会出现，当N%K==0的时候，其中K=K%N(如果K&gt;N,实际上还是相当于K%N,因为移动N+1个位置就相当于移动1个位置)循环替换多次后，一定会产生再次回到最初开始的位置上的问题，程序就进入死循环。此时，我们需要做的是将从一开始的元素的下一个元素开始继续这个过程。<br>详细的说就是一开始从i=0开始替换，并且保存每次被替换的元素，便于下次替换时候用上次被替换的元素去替换它应该替换的元素。i=0所在的元素替换i+k%N所在的元素，并且再次保存被替换的元素的值，此时替换的都是i%K==0的元素，并且因为每隔K替换一次，所以已经有N/K个元素确定位置了，当回到最初开始的元素时，就从开始的元素的下一个继续进行这个过程，此时就是i%k==1的元素在进行替换工作了，直到回到i%k==0的元素位置上，此时i==k,那么一共确定位置的就有k乘以N/K个元素了，刚刚好N个元素，所有位置都在指定的位置上。<br>过程如下，红线表示第一个阶段，i%k==0，绿线表示第二个阶段，i%k==1，两个阶段，每隔阶段(N=6/K=2)=3，2乘以3=6.所有元素归位<br><img src=\"/2019/08/07/旋转数组/image.png\" alt=\"image\"><br>代码如下：<br><figure class=\"highlight plain\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br><span class=\"line\">11</span><br><span class=\"line\">12</span><br><span class=\"line\">13</span><br><span class=\"line\">14</span><br><span class=\"line\">15</span><br><span class=\"line\">16</span><br><span class=\"line\">17</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">class Solution:</span><br><span class=\"line\">    def rotate(self, nums: List[int], k: int) -&gt; None:</span><br><span class=\"line\">        count=0</span><br><span class=\"line\">        staIndex=0;#起点</span><br><span class=\"line\">        while(count&lt;len(nums)):</span><br><span class=\"line\">            preValue=nums[staIndex];#预先值，即是将要放入确定位置的值</span><br><span class=\"line\">            curIndex=(staIndex+k)%len(nums);#当前可能需要被替换的值</span><br><span class=\"line\">            while(staIndex!=curIndex):#没有回到最初位置就继续循环</span><br><span class=\"line\">                temp=nums.pop(curIndex);#插入</span><br><span class=\"line\">                nums.insert(curIndex,preValue);</span><br><span class=\"line\">                preValue=temp;#更新数值</span><br><span class=\"line\">                count+=1;</span><br><span class=\"line\">                curIndex=(curIndex+k)%len(nums);</span><br><span class=\"line\">            nums.pop(curIndex);#插入本阶段最后数值后继续下一个阶段直到count=len（nums）即是所有数都放置在最终位置</span><br><span class=\"line\">            nums.insert(curIndex,preValue);</span><br><span class=\"line\">            count+=1;</span><br><span class=\"line\">            staIndex+=1;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>\n<p>时间复杂度：O(N)<br>空间复杂度：O(1)</p>\n","categories":[],"tags":[]}